er:description\" content=\"AI-driven creative work for brands and businesses. Fast, smart, and uniquely yours.\"/><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/03~yq9q893hmn.js\" noModule=\"\"></script></head><body class=\"min-h-screen antialiased\"><div hidden=\"\"><!--$--><!--/$--></div><header class=\"fixed top-0 left-0 right-0 z-50 h-[72px] transition-all duration-300 bg-transparent\"><div class=\"max-w-[1160px] mx-auto px-6 flex items-center justify-between h-full\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"font-display font-extrabold text-xl text-white\">Ringo<span class=\"text-violet-400\">.</span></a><nav class=\"flex items-center gap-8\"><a href=\"#services\" class=\"text-sm text-white/50 hover:text-white transition-colors hidden sm:block\">Services</a><a href=\"#work\" class=\"text-sm text-white/50 hover:text-white transition-colors hidden sm:block\">Work</a><a href=\"#about\" class=\"text-sm text-white/50 hover:text-white transition-colors hidden sm:block\">About</a><a href=\"#contact\" class=\"text-sm font-semibold px-5 py-2.5 rounded-full bg-violet-500 hover:bg-violet-400 text-white transition-colors\">Let&#x27;s Talk</a></nav></div></header><main><section class=\"relative pt-[152px] pb-24 overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"absolute top-[-100px] right-[-200px] w-[700px] h-[700px] bg-violet-600/10 rounded-full blur-3xl pointer-events-none\"></div><div class=\"relative z-10 max-w-[1160px] mx-auto px-6\"><div class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-violet-500/10 border border-violet-500/25 text-violet-400 text-xs font-medium px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full mb-7\">✦ AI Creative Studio · Toronto, 2026</div><h1 class=\"font-display font-extrabold text-5xl sm:text-6xl lg:text-[76px] leading-[1.08] text-white mb-6 max-w-[720px]\">We build creative work<!-- --> <span class=\"bg-gradient-to-r from-violet-400 via-purple-400 to-pink-400 bg-clip-text text-transparent\">powered by Ringo Innovation.</span></h1><p class=\"text-lg text-white/50 max-w-[520px] mb-10 leading-relaxed\">Ringo Innovations brings fresh AI-driven thinking to brand visuals, content, and digital experiences — so you get output that&#x27;s faster, smarter, and uniquely yours.</p><div class=\"flex flex-wrap gap-4\"><a href=\"#contact\" class=\"inline-flex items-center px-7 py-3.5 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-r from-violet-500 to-purple-500 text-white font-semibold text-[15px] shadow-[0_0_32px_rgba(139,92,246,0.4)] hover:shadow-[0_0_48px_rgba(139,92,246,0.6)] hover:-translate-y-0.5 transition-all\">Start a Project</a><a href=\"#services\" class=\"inline-flex items-center px-7 py-3.5 rounded-full border border-white/10 text-white/50 font-semibold text-[15px] hover:border-white/25 hover:text-white transition-all\">See What We Do ↓</a></div></div></section><section id=\"services\" class=\"py-24 border-t border-white/8 max-w-[1160px] mx-auto px-6\"><div class=\"text-xs font-semibold tracking-widest uppercase text-violet-400 mb-3\">What We Do</div><h2 class=\"font-display font-extrabold text-4xl lg:text-[44px] text-white mb-4\">AI-Driven Creative Services</h2><p class=\"text-[17px] text-white/50 mb-12\">Every project is custom. Here&#x27;s how we typically help.</p><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-5\"><div class=\"bg-white/[0.04] border border-white/8 rounded-2xl p-8 hover:border-violet-500/35 hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-200\"><div class=\"text-[28px] mb-4\">🎨</div><h3 class=\"text-[17px] font-semibold text-white mb-2.5\">Visual Content Creation</h3><p class=\"text-sm text-white/50 leading-relaxed\">AI-assisted graphics, social media visuals, and brand assets — produced fast without sacrificing quality.</p></div><div class=\"bg-white/[0.04] border border-white/8 rounded-2xl p-8 hover:border-violet-500/35 hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-200\"><div class=\"text-[28px] mb-4\">✍️</div><h3 class=\"text-[17px] font-semibold text-white mb-2.5\">AI Copywriting &amp; Content</h3><p class=\"text-sm text-white/50 leading-relaxed\">Website copy, blog posts, product descriptions, and marketing scripts crafted with AI and refined by human judgment.</p></div><div class=\"bg-white/[0.04] border border-white/8 rounded-2xl p-8 hover:border-violet-500/35 hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-200\"><div class=\"text-[28px] mb-4\">🤖</div><h3 class=\"text-[17px] font-semibold text-white mb-2.5\">AI Workflow Automation</h3><p class=\"text-sm text-white/50 leading-relaxed\">Custom AI pipelines and prompt systems that cut repetitive creative work out of your team&#x27;s day.</p></div><div class=\"bg-white/[0.04] border border-white/8 rounded-2xl p-8 hover:border-violet-500/35 hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-200\"><div class=\"text-[28px] mb-4\">🌐</div><h3 class=\"text-[17px] font-semibold text-white mb-2.5\">Web &amp; Digital Presence</h3><p class=\"text-sm text-white/50 leading-relaxed\">Landing pages, portfolios, and microsites built cleanly and quickly — designed to convert.</p></div><div class=\"bg-white/[0.04] border border-white/8 rounded-2xl p-8 hover:border-violet-500/35 hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-200\"><div class=\"text-[28px] mb-4\">💡</div><h3 class=\"text-[17px] font-semibold text-white mb-2.5\">Brand Strategy with AI</h3><p class=\"text-sm text-white/50 leading-relaxed\">From naming and positioning to tone-of-voice guides — AI-augmented thinking to sharpen your brand story.</p></div><div class=\"bg-white/[0.04] border border-white/8 rounded-2xl p-8 hover:border-violet-500/35 hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-200\"><div class=\"text-[28px] mb-4\">📊</div><h3 class=\"text-[17px] font-semibold text-white mb-2.5\">Custom AI Consulting</h3><p class=\"text-sm text-white/50 leading-relaxed\">Not sure where AI fits? We&#x27;ll map the opportunities, build a plan, and help you act on it.</p></div></div></section><section id=\"work\" class=\"py-24 border-t border-white/8\"><div class=\"max-w-[1160px] mx-auto px-6\"><div class=\"text-xs font-semibold tracking-widest uppercase text-violet-400 mb-3\">Our Work</div><h2 class=\"font-display font-extrabold text-4xl lg:text-[44px] text-white mb-4\">Things we&#x27;ve built.</h2><p class=\"text-[17px] text-white/50 mb-12\">Real projects. Real outcomes.</p><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6\"><a href=\"https://mood-journal-6g5buj02j-ringo-innovations.vercel.app/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"group bg-gradient-to-br from-violet-500/20 to-pink-500/10 border border-white/8 hover:border-violet-500/40 rounded-2xl p-8 flex flex-col gap-4 transition-all duration-200 hover:-translate-y-1\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between\"><span class=\"text-xs font-semibold tracking-wider uppercase text-violet-400 bg-violet-500/10 border border-violet-500/20 px-3 py-1 rounded-full\">AI · Web App</span><span class=\"text-white/20 group-hover:text-white/60 transition-colors text-lg\">↗</span></div><h3 class=\"text-xl font-semibold text-white\">Mood Journal</h3><p class=\"text-sm text-white/50 leading-relaxed flex-1\">An AI-powered mood journaling app that helps users track emotions, identify patterns, and gain personal insights through intelligent reflection.</p><span class=\"text-sm text-violet-400 font-medium group-hover:underline\">View Project →</span></a><a href=\"https://habit-tracker-mocha-ten.vercel.app/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"group bg-gradient-to-br from-emerald-500/20 to-teal-500/10 border border-white/8 hover:border-emerald-500/40 rounded-2xl p-8 flex flex-col gap-4 transition-all duration-200 hover:-translate-y-1\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between\"><span class=\"text-xs font-semibold tracking-wider uppercase text-violet-400 bg-violet-500/10 border border-violet-500/20 px-3 py-1 rounded-full\">Productivity · Web App</span><span class=\"text-white/20 group-hover:text-white/60 transition-colors text-lg\">↗</span></div><h3 class=\"text-xl font-semibold text-white\">Habit Tracker</h3><p class=\"text-sm text-white/50 leading-relaxed flex-1\">A clean habit tracking app that helps users build consistency, visualize streaks, and stay accountable to their daily goals.</p><span class=\"text-sm text-violet-400 font-medium group-hover:underline\">View Project →</span></a><a href=\"https://photo-pick-ai.vercel.app/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"group bg-gradient-to-br from-sky-500/20 to-blue-500/10 border border-white/8 hover:border-sky-500/40 rounded-2xl p-8 flex flex-col gap-4 transition-all duration-200 hover:-translate-y-1\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between\"><span class=\"text-xs font-semibold tracking-wider uppercase text-violet-400 bg-violet-500/10 border border-violet-500/20 px-3 py-1 rounded-full\">AI · Photo Tool</span><span class=\"text-white/20 group-hover:text-white/60 transition-colors text-lg\">↗</span></div><h3 class=\"text-xl font-semibold text-white\">Photo Pick AI</h3><p class=\"text-sm text-white/50 leading-relaxed flex-1\">An AI-powered photo selection tool that automatically picks the best shots from a batch — saving time and delivering standout results.</p><span class=\"text-sm text-violet-400 font-medium group-hover:underline\">View Project →</span></a><div class=\"border border-dashed border-white/10 rounded-2xl p-8 flex flex-col items-center justify-center gap-3 text-center min-h-[220px]\"><div class=\"text-3xl opacity-30\">+</div><p class=\"text-sm text-white/25\">More coming soon</p></div></div></div></section><section class=\"py-24 bg-white/[0.02] border-y border-white/8\"><div class=\"max-w-[1160px] mx-auto px-6 grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-20 items-center\"><div><div class=\"text-xs font-semibold tracking-widest uppercase text-violet-400 mb-3\">Why Ringo</div><h2 class=\"font-display font-extrabold text-4xl lg:text-[44px] text-white mb-8\">Fresh thinking.<br/>Real results.</h2><ul class=\"space-y-7\"><li class=\"flex gap-4 items-start\"><span class=\"shrink-0 w-7 h-7 rounded-full bg-violet-500/15 border border-violet-500/30 flex items-center justify-center text-[11px] text-violet-400 mt-0.5\">✓</span><div><strong class=\"block text-[15px] text-white mb-1\">Speed without compromise</strong><p class=\"text-sm text-white/50\">AI lets us move faster than traditional agencies — without cutting corners on craft.</p></div></li><li class=\"flex gap-4 items-start\"><span class=\"shrink-0 w-7 h-7 rounded-full bg-violet-500/15 border border-violet-500/30 flex items-center justify-center text-[11px] text-violet-400 mt-0.5\">✓</span><div><strong class=\"block text-[15px] text-white mb-1\">Direct founder involvement</strong><p class=\"text-sm text-white/50\">You work with me directly. No account managers, no hand-offs, no lost context.</p></div></li><li class=\"flex gap-4 items-start\"><span class=\"shrink-0 w-7 h-7 rounded-full bg-violet-500/15 border border-violet-500/30 flex items-center justify-center text-[11px] text-violet-400 mt-0.5\">✓</span><div><strong class=\"block text-[15px] text-white mb-1\">Honest pricing</strong><p class=\"text-sm text-white/50\">Startup-friendly rates. Transparent scope. No surprise invoices.</p></div></li><li class=\"flex gap-4 items-start\"><span class=\"shrink-0 w-7 h-7 rounded-full bg-violet-500/15 border border-violet-500/30 flex items-center justify-center text-[11px] text-violet-400 mt-0.5\">✓</span><div><strong class=\"block text-[15px] text-white mb-1\">Flexible engagement</strong><p class=\"text-sm text-white/50\">One-off projects, monthly retainers, or ongoing partnerships — whatever fits your needs.</p></div></li></ul></div><div class=\"flex flex-col gap-4\"><div class=\"bg-white/[0.04] border border-white/8 rounded-2xl p-7 flex items-center gap-6 \"><div class=\"font-display font-extrabold text-[42px] bg-gradient-to-br from-violet-400 to-purple-400 bg-clip-text text-transparent shrink-0\">3×</div><div class=\"text-sm text-white/50 leading-relaxed whitespace-pre-line\">Faster delivery\nvs. traditional agencies</div></div><div class=\"bg-white/[0.04] border border-white/8 rounded-2xl p-7 flex items-center gap-6 lg:ml-8\"><div class=\"font-display font-extrabold text-[42px] bg-gradient-to-br from-violet-400 to-purple-400 bg-clip-text text-transparent shrink-0\">AI</div><div class=\"text-sm text-white/50 leading-relaxed whitespace-pre-line\">First approach on\nevery project</div></div><div class=\"bg-white/[0.04] border border-white/8 rounded-2xl p-7 flex items-center gap-6 \"><div class=\"font-display font-extrabold text-[42px] bg-gradient-to-br from-violet-400 to-purple-400 bg-clip-text text-transparent shrink-0\">1:1</div><div class=\"text-sm text-white/50 leading-relaxed whitespace-pre-line\">Direct access to\nthe founder</div></div></div></div></section><section id=\"about\" class=\"py-24 border-t border-white/8\"><div class=\"max-w-[1160px] mx-auto px-6 grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-[1fr_2fr] gap-20 items-center\"><div class=\"max-w-[280px] mx-auto lg:mx-0 w-full\"><div class=\"aspect-square rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-br from-violet-500/20 to-purple-500/10 border border-violet-500/25 flex items-center justify-center font-display font-extrabold text-5xl text-violet-400\">RI</div></div><div><div class=\"text-xs font-semibold tracking-widest uppercase text-violet-400 mb-3\">About</div><h2 class=\"font-display font-extrabold text-4xl lg:text-[44px] text-white mb-6\">Built by a founder<br/>who actually builds.</h2><p class=\"text-[16px] text-white/50 leading-[1.8] mb-4\">Ringo Innovations was founded in Toronto in April 2026 with a simple belief: AI should make creative work more human, not less. I started this company fresh — no corporate background, no huge team — just a strong drive to help businesses unlock what AI can really do for their creative output.</p><p class=\"text-[16px] text-white/50 leading-[1.8] mb-8\">I&#x27;m still early in the journey, which means you get someone who is hungry, attentive, and genuinely invested in making your project succeed. Every client right now matters enormously to me — and that shows in the work.</p><a href=\"#contact\" class=\"inline-flex items-center px-7 py-3.5 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-r from-violet-500 to-purple-500 text-white font-semibold text-[15px] shadow-[0_0_32px_rgba(139,92,246,0.35)] hover:shadow-[0_0_48px_rgba(139,92,246,0.5)] hover:-translate-y-0.5 transition-all\">Work With Me</a></div></div></section><section class=\"py-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-violet-500/15 to-purple-500/8 border-y border-violet-500/20 text-center\"><div class=\"max-w-[1160px] mx-auto px-6\"><h2 class=\"font-display font-extrabold text-4xl lg:text-[44px] text-white mb-3\">Have a project in mind?</h2><p class=\"text-[17px] text-white/50 mb-8\">Let&#x27;s talk about what AI can do for your creative work.</p><a href=\"#contact\" class=\"inline-flex items-center px-7 py-3.5 rounded-full bg-white text-[#0a0a0f] font-semibold text-[15px] hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:shadow-[0_8px_32px_rgba(255,255,255,0.15)] transition-all\">Get in Touch</a></div></section><section id=\"contact\" class=\"py-24 border-t border-white/8\"><div class=\"max-w-[1160px] mx-auto px-6 grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-[1fr_1.4fr] gap-20 items-start\"><div><div class=\"text-xs font-semibold tracking-widest uppercase text-violet-400 mb-3\">Contact</div><h2 class=\"font-display font-extrabold text-4xl lg:text-[44px] text-white mb-4\">Let&#x27;s start something.</h2><p class=\"text-[16px] text-white/50 leading-relaxed mb-8\">Tell me about your project and I&#x27;ll get back to you within 24 hours.</p><div class=\"space-y-3\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-3 text-[15px] text-white/50\"><span>📍</span> Toronto, Canada</div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-3 text-[15px] text-white/50\"><span>📧</span><a href=\"mailto:ringo144516@gmail.com\" class=\"text-violet-400 hover:underline\">h-fujishima@ringo-innovations.com</a></div></div></div><form class=\"space-y-5\" action=\"mailto:ringo144516@gmail.com\" encType=\"text/plain\" method=\"get\"><div class=\"grid gr